title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS Isuzu D-MAX 4JJ1TCX 3.0L 2012-on CRD 130kW Diesel – Pre Filter Separator Kit Fuel Manager FM601DPK

content.rendered:
Fuel Manager FM601DPK Pre Filter Separator Kit for:
IIsuzu D-MAX II 3.0L Diesel 4JJ1TCX CRD 130kW 2012-on
CRD Diesel Single Battery 130kW

This filter unit is to be used as a Pre-Filter to separate water and contaminates thus avoiding costly repairs due to poor fuel quality. Comes complete with very specific fitting instructions and mounting bracket so all of the hard work is done !

Kit FM601DPK Includes:
Fuel Manager 30 Micron Filtration Unit
Mounting Bolts, Washers & Nyloc Nuts
Spare 30 Micron Replacement Filter
Quality Fuel Hose
Direction Plus Filter Bracket
Brass 1/2″ Barb Fittings
2x 90 Degree Brass Elbows
3x 6mm Bolt & Washer
Blanking Plugs
Hose Clamps
Thread Paste Sealant (6ml Tube)
Thread Paste Sealant (6ml Tube)

Download PDF Info >

Install all fittings and plugs with the thread paste.
